  "title": "Warehouse Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong><br>\n</strong>Our client is a global leader in gateway services, who is seeking to recruit a <strong>Warehouse Technician (Location: East)</strong>. This position is based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Warehouse Technician (Location: East)</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>You will be part of a team responsible for the maintenance of material handling equipment, forklifts, tractors, equipment and various systems at the warehouse. You will perform trouble shooting functions and undertake basic repair work. Working jointly with our vendors, you will assist to ensure that operations are not disrupted due to breakdowns of the equipment within the warehouse.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Nitec in Electrical Engineering or equivalent</p>\n<p>· Possess basic computer skills and knowledge of Microsoft Office</p>\n<p>· Able to work in harsh environments such as cold rooms, high humidity, wet conditions and steamy environment and also able to work at high ground</p>\n<p>· Can work on rotating shifts or weekends, if required</p>\n<p><strong>Others:</strong></p>\n<p>· Shift allowances and OT pay applicable.</p>\n<p>· Staff transport will be provided for candidates working beyond midnight.</p>\n<p>· Work Week &amp; Shift:<strong> </strong>6 days, rotating shift</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JJ Consulting Services</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to <strong>jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg</strong> stating position applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br>\n<br>\nWe thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
